⭐ איכות: ${(cacheData.analytics?.hit_rate_percent || cacheData.status?.hitRate || 0) > 80 ? 'Excellent' : (cacheData.analytics?.hit_rate_percent || cacheData.status?.hitRate || 0) > 50 ? 'Good' : 'Needs improvement'}

